</p>
<h2>judging criteria</h2>
<p>
  The judges will base their decisions on three main criteria:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>Execution (50%)</li>
	<li>Innovation (30%)</li>
	<li>Experience (20%)</li>
</ul>
<p>
  <strong>Execution</strong> evaluates how well the team has implemented the idea into a functional application.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Innovation</strong> considers the originality of the idea and how it applies to the theme.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>Experience</strong> is a measure of the usability and design of the application.
</p>
